sql:
SELECT DISTINCT t.teacher_details
FROM Teachers t
JOIN Classes c ON t.teacher_id = c.teacher_id
JOIN (
    SELECT student_id
    FROM Transcripts
    ORDER BY date_of_transcript
    LIMIT 1
) earliest_student ON c.student_id = earliest_student.student_id;
question: Find the details of the teachers who have taught the student with the earliest transcript issuance.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT T.teacher_details
FROM Teachers T
JOIN Classes C ON T.teacher_id = C.teacher_id
WHERE C.student_id = (
    SELECT student_id
    FROM Transcripts
    WHERE date_of_transcript = (
        SELECT MIN(date_of_transcript) FROM Transcripts
    )
    LIMIT 1
)
question: Find the details of the teachers who have taught the student with the earliest transcript issuance.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT T.teacher_details
FROM Transcripts TR
JOIN Classes C ON TR.student_id = C.student_id
JOIN Teachers T ON C.teacher_id = T.teacher_id
WHERE TR.date_of_transcript = (SELECT MIN(date_of_transcript) FROM Transcripts)
